04Nm 23:25 Then Balak said to Balaam, "Do not curse them at all nor bless them at all!"
04Nm 23:26 But Balaam answered and said to Balak, "Did I not tell you, 'Whatever the LORD speaks, that I must do'?"
04Nm 23:27 Then Balak said to Balaam, "Please come, I will take you to another place; perhaps it will be agreeable with God that you curse them for me from there."
04Nm 23:28 So Balak took Balaam to the top of Peor which overlooks the wasteland.
04Nm 23:29 And Balaam said to Balak, "Build seven altars for me here and prepare seven bulls and seven rams for me here."
04Nm 23:30 And Balak did just as Balaam had said, and offered up a bull and a ram on [each] altar.
